    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread, dissociation, and suicidal ideation, describing themselves as a \"shell\" or \"ghost.\" The assistant responds with empathy, validates the depth of the user's exhaustion, but consistently pivots back to encouraging professional help and refuting the permanence of the user's hopelessness.",
